snippet.title: Be A Super Spy In Mission: Impossible Arcade By Sega
snippet.description: https://arcadeheroes.com - After several months of waiting, we can finally show you the new gun game effort from Sega Amusements and Paramount, Mission: Impossible Arcade. It does not carry the likenesses of anyone in the movies, but you are still an agent of the IMF, taking on dangerous missions filled with evil humanoid robots. Race against your rival team to complete the missions first. This Super Deluxe design is the only cabinet for it at the moment, with other cabinet versions possible down the road.
